              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-footer">
              <div class="feature-metrics">
                <span class="metric">Highly Customizable</span>
                <span class="metric-sep">‚Ä¢</span>
                <span class="metric">Server-Specific</span>
              </div>
            </div>
